alignItems.description: Placement of child elements in a direction not specified by flex-direction

animationDuration.description: Time required to complete one animation cycle

justifyContent.description: Alignment of child elements in the direction specified by flex-direction

marginLeft.description: The left margin of the outside of the element

marginTop.description: The top margin of the outside of the element

opacity.description: Opacity of the element, i.e., the degree to which the content behind the element is hidden

padding.description: Width of additional area created inside the element

paddingLeft.description: Width of the left margin within the element's interior

hoverStyle.description: Object representing the style on hover
